<h3 id="Armor12or3" class="quick-menu-exclude compendium-hr heading-anchor" data-content-chunk-id="66d12a25-7484-46b6-9e9b-983a9ad63299"><a href="#Armor12or3" data-content-chunk-id="19e67173-440d-489f-9162-75c0c8ed4aa4"></a><span class="Serif-Character-Style_Bold-Italic-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="3384f628-c3cf-4d67-8158-b730d3d88cf6">Armor, +1, +2, or +3</span></h3>
<p class="Core-Styles_Core-Metadata" data-content-chunk-id="ebcdfed6-ae7f-446f-86ea-1bc0c169ea9d">Armor (light, medium, or heavy), rare (+1), very rare (+2), or legendary (+3)</p>
<p class="Core-Styles_Core-Body" data-content-chunk-id="de75fd76-0bad-476f-977e-f6312a227479">You have a bonus to AC while wearing this armor. The bonus is determined by i<span class="No-Break" data-content-chunk-id="30bf2162-2fe2-4263-95bd-80eb9d331603">ts rarity.</span></p>
<h3 id="ArmorofInvulnerability" class="quick-menu-exclude compendium-hr heading-anchor" data-content-chunk-id="d4129553-b70a-48f0-aea2-d54347536ea9"><a href="#ArmorofInvulnerability" data-content-chunk-id="f044ffe9-d128-44c1-90d5-b34095de66a7"></a><a class="tooltip-hover magic-item-tooltip" href="/magic-items/4574-armor-of-invulnerability" data-tooltip-href="/magic-items/4574-tooltip">Armor of Invulnerability</a></h3>
<p class="Core-Styles_Core-Metadata" data-content-chunk-id="fbbd5bd9-15dc-42db-b25f-d75e8b85133f">Armor (plate), legendary (requires attunement)</p>
<p class="Core-Styles_Core-Body" data-content-chunk-id="a693f242-9ec5-4ecb-93d4-b6fd4ac22512">You have resistance to nonmagical damage while you wear this armor. Additionally, you can use an action to make yourself immune to nonmagical damage for 10 minutes or until you are no longer wearing the armor. Once this special action is used, it can’t be used again until the <span class="No-Break" data-content-chunk-id="66a22ef3-7c0f-45e4-98d6-c74ae829f95a">next dawn.</span></p>
<h3 id="ArmorofResistance" class="quick-menu-exclude compendium-hr heading-anchor" data-content-chunk-id="9acef2f3-88ff-450c-b34e-d9d786a0f15a"><a href="#ArmorofResistance" data-content-chunk-id="51f96a17-423d-452f-8dc0-c62772466a68"></a><a class="tooltip-hover magic-item-tooltip" href="/magic-items/5371-armor-of-resistance" data-tooltip-href="/magic-items/5371-tooltip">Armor of Resistance</a></h3>
<p class="Core-Styles_Core-Metadata" data-content-chunk-id="f604d09f-ac0c-484e-a5bc-54e66669f5cc">Armor (light, medium, or heavy), rare (requires attunement)</p>
<p class="Core-Styles_Core-Body" data-content-chunk-id="9ee5fe60-923d-4c85-b504-22dc98f3f732">You have resistance to one type of damage while you wear this armor. The DM chooses the type or determines it randomly from the opti<span class="No-Break" data-content-chunk-id="69ced23c-f547-4414-94ef-8e3e2b662333">ons below.</span></p>
<table data-content-chunk-id="69b30c9b-6d5f-45a6-bbb8-fbddf1c437e5">
