<h3 id="ElementalGem" class="quick-menu-exclude compendium-hr heading-anchor" data-content-chunk-id="7825cac9-9592-4d68-b7c3-a6c7e3672bf1"><a href="#ElementalGem" data-content-chunk-id="eae35106-5713-48f3-8910-ba22ce9218b9"></a><a class="tooltip-hover magic-item-tooltip" href="/magic-items/5374-elemental-gem" data-tooltip-href="/magic-items/5374-tooltip">Elemental Gem</a></h3>
<p class="Core-Styles_Core-Metadata" data-content-chunk-id="981f181b-2b85-498a-b4b5-1a41715b0cb4">Wondrous item, uncommon</p>
<p class="Core-Styles_Core-Body" data-content-chunk-id="d3ef3e7f-a657-45c8-9698-c9da8ff9eb65">This gem contains a mote of elemental energy. When you use an action to break the gem, an elemental is summoned as if you had cast the <span class="Serif-Character-Style_Italic-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="3b993f77-4a34-44fc-aa50-d9578ba1fc2d"><a class="tooltip-hover spell-tooltip" href="/spells/conjure-elemental" data-tooltip-href="/spells/2041-tooltip">conjure elemental</a></span> spell, and the gem’s magic is lost. The type of gem determines the elemental summoned by <span class="No-Break" data-content-chunk-id="57192c88-a819-4bf2-98b8-776fb7a019ec">the spell.</span></p>
