<h3 id="PotionofSpeed" class="quick-menu-exclude compendium-hr heading-anchor" data-content-chunk-id="9586c151-e898-43e1-a3cb-334cfb812acf"><a href="#PotionofSpeed" data-content-chunk-id="fa835eb5-098e-45a0-8eaa-589ba6d9cc29"></a><a class="tooltip-hover magic-item-tooltip" href="/magic-items/4714-potion-of-speed" data-tooltip-href="/magic-items/4714-tooltip">Potion of Speed</a></h3>
