<li class="Core-Styles_Core-Bulleted" data-content-chunk-id="e9db1347-ada4-42ff-bffc-af3fa9e20fb7">You can breathe underwater and have a swimming speed equal to your walk<span class="No-Break" data-content-chunk-id="68f74519-9561-4cb2-b68d-2fd240a6fb61">ing speed.</span></li>
<li class="Core-Styles_Core-Bulleted" data-content-chunk-id="e949f0ed-1582-4b99-85c7-900a204537c7">You can cast the following spells from the ring, expending the necessary number of charges: <span class="Serif-Character-Style_Italic-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="0f83c134-f806-40a8-8e81-491678cafd90"><a class="tooltip-hover spell-tooltip" href="/spells/create-or-destroy-water" data-tooltip-href="/spells/2053-tooltip">create or destroy water</a></span> (1 charge), <span class="Serif-Character-Style_Italic-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="9bdeb9af-ddd3-4dea-87a9-10555fdb7ba2"><a class="tooltip-hover spell-tooltip" href="/spells/control-water" data-tooltip-href="/spells/2049-tooltip">control water</a></span> (3 charges), <span class="Serif-Character-Style_Italic-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="88606c39-c91d-4eaf-8d1c-c672161ff32d"><a class="tooltip-hover spell-tooltip" href="/spells/ice-storm" data-tooltip-href="/spells/2151-tooltip">ice storm</a></span> (2 charges), or <span class="Serif-Character-Style_Italic-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="3c04f6ec-2ad2-4e09-ae44-51c62d4aca6b"><a class="tooltip-hover spell-tooltip" href="/spells/wall-of-ice" data-tooltip-href="/spells/2293-tooltip">wall of ice</a></span> (3<span class="No-Break" data-content-chunk-id="8efe8808-e422-4abf-a4c1-a9b720ce462e"> charges).</span></li>
