<h3 id="RingofResistance" class="quick-menu-exclude compendium-hr heading-anchor" data-content-chunk-id="2c88a484-3f7b-4889-abc7-e7cab6ccfb1b"><a href="#RingofResistance" data-content-chunk-id="38c1e0da-4ea6-431d-8769-7176ddf542e7"></a><a class="tooltip-hover magic-item-tooltip" href="/magic-items/5420-ring-of-resistance" data-tooltip-href="/magic-items/5420-tooltip">Ring of Resistance</a></h3>
