<h3 id="WandofSecrets" class="quick-menu-exclude compendium-hr heading-anchor" data-content-chunk-id="0a6f204c-8726-4241-bea5-f2b66c1a13e2"><a href="#WandofSecrets" data-content-chunk-id="9b2e1f9e-183a-42f0-8a2a-d000f68084af"></a><a class="tooltip-hover magic-item-tooltip" href="/magic-items/4797-wand-of-secrets" data-tooltip-href="/magic-items/4797-tooltip">Wand of Secrets</a></h3>
